                                <li>It is wise to book early for this reason, to get the most favorable rates, and to confirm that your pet is allowed.</li>
                                <li>At times, airplane companies may have offers or discounts of some sort that may be useful for your trip. Moreover, you will have the best deals and offers if you book tickets through the website.</li>
